Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.78,0:00:04.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The rhythm of the wind clears reasoning,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.72,0:00:06.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Always confirming that vital clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.59,0:00:08.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The secret behind the mystery is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.45,0:00:10.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We just have to get to the professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.86,0:00:12.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Recognizing that single truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.66,0:00:14.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A child with the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.73,0:00:16.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.25,0:01:52.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.42,0:01:54.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.69,0:01:57.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In my pocket...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.09,0:02:00.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've got a lead to the Black Organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.60,0:02:07.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll analyze every bit of this disk on the professor's computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.90,0:02:09.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Conan-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.47,0:02:13.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder if people change.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.81,0:02:18.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do hearts grow apart if they're separated?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.55,0:02:25.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All I can do is keep waiting...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.22,0:02:28.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.96,0:02:36.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But don't worry, I'm sure Shinichi-niichan\Nis just how you remember him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.13,0:02:40.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure there's nothing to worry...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.94,0:02:45.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wish you were Shinichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.05,0:02:54.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Silly me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.68,0:02:55.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What am I saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.92,0:02:57.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.45,0:02:59.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.42,0:03:02.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's really me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.46,0:03:06.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't, I can't tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.79,0:03:09.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not until I get them...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.26,0:03:13.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Until I take them out...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.73,0:03:16.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I mustn't tell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.56,0:03:42.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.60,0:03:52.34,Title,,0,0,0,,Contact with the Black Organization\N (Negotiation Part){Title}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.03,0:03:49.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Contact with the Black Organization: Negotiation Part!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.16,0:04:14.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're crying again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.16,0:04:16.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.96,0:04:20.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're always crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.53,0:04:21.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Always?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.30,0:04:25.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.08,0:04:40.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it just occurred to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.65,0:04:44.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You remind me of a woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.76,0:04:49.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One who always cries in the dark trying to appear normal...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.33,0:04:52.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A foolish woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.83,0:04:53.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A foolish woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.24,0:05:01.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ran-neechan...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.77,0:05:04.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you know that man?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.04,0:05:09.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I met him when I went to New York with Shinichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.91,0:05:15.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was while I was wailing for Shinichi\Nin front of an abandoned building.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.28,0:05:20.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He came up to me and asked if I had seen\Na Japanese man with long, silver hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.63,0:05:31.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The building where that serial killer was hiding!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.10,0:05:35.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I don't think he's a bad man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.24,0:05:36.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.27,0:05:42.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw him with one of his friends that had a\Njacket with "F.B.I." written on the back, I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.25,0:05:46.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,F.B.I.?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.55,0:05:50.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nonsense, an F.B.I. agent in Japan...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.18,0:05:51.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.22,0:05:56.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no, he's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.66,0:06:05.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Conan-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.17,0:06:16.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, that guy... Is he really with the F.B.I.?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.14,0:06:22.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That killer was murdered then, he didn't commit suicide...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.82,0:06:28.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With the F.B.I. nearby, no one could have killed him then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.09,0:06:29.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.09,0:06:35.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,During James-san's kidnapping case, the\Nway Haibara reacted to his presence...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.40,0:06:40.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What if he's the one who killed that serial killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.64,0:06:46.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe he's involved in Haibara's past...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.41,0:06:51.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akai Shuichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.88,0:06:56.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be, he's actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.15,0:07:05.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Conan-kun, what do you want for\Ndinner tonight? Sashimi? Tian Jin?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.69,0:07:08.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your favorite beef stew?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.09,0:07:10.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't cook all three.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.99,0:07:13.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Conan-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.70,0:07:17.20,Signs,,0,0,0,,l promised play games\N with the professor\NI'll be staying over there tonight\N- Conan{Sign}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.17,0:07:24.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"l -promised play games with the professor.\NI'll be staying over there tonight."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.08,0:07:27.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Games again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.58,0:07:31.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jeez, such a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.65,0:07:41.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My priority right now is this disk, not Akai Shuichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.76,0:07:44.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the diary of someone involved with the Organization...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.93,0:07:47.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Itakuro-san had actually met with Tequila.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.70,0:07:51.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't miss a single bit from this disk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.74,0:07:55.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll discover their objectives and their identities!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.74,0:07:59.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Their true identities!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.91,0:08:07.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Shinichi, perfect timing. I've invented a new gadget for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.22,0:08:13.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, here's a pair of extra Homing Glasses, so\Nyou don't have to recharge them anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.39,0:08:15.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, where's Haibara?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.39,0:08:18.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ai-kun's in the shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.96,0:08:21.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's great news.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.73,0:08:27.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shinichi, don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.94,0:08:29.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yau plan go peep on her!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.27,0:08:32.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.84,0:08:37.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? You've got a lead to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.71,0:08:39.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that true, Shinichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.45,0:08:39.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.68,0:08:43.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haibara will definitely be upset to know about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.25,0:08:46.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's finish up before she gets out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.89,0:08:50.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see, two years ago... Two years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.33,0:08:51.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.29,0:08:52.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.33,0:08:58.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,March 7th: "A giant speaking Kansai-ben\Nvisited today without an appointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.80,0:09:02.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"He seemed very interested in the\Nsystem pragram I was working on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.34,0:09:08.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"When I told him I had stepped working on\Nit since my vision was declining, he left.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.61,0:09:14.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"That man dressed all in black... I hope I never see him again."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.11,0:09:16.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, is that all?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.85,0:09:23.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It doesn't seem like there's any further mention that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.99,0:09:27.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jeez, I went through so much trouble copy this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.96,0:09:32.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All I know is they were interested in a\Nprogram Itakura-san was developing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.80,0:09:35.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I really don't know what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.70,0:09:41.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But jeez, this ltakura guy isn't exactly very neat, is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.64,0:09:45.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, the amount of space between each entry is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.18,0:09:49.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd make it consistent if I were keeping a diary.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.95,0:09:52.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.55,0:09:58.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said Itakura-san was always very picky.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.39,0:10:01.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not it, Professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.39,0:10:05.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not that he isn't neat...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.46,0:10:07.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.10,0:10:12.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And drag the mouse to highlight it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.41,0:10:15.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-This
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.87,0:10:21.38,Signs,,0,0,0,,I'm tired...\NAt this rate, I may be killed...\NSometime in the near future... {Sign-Middle Paragraph}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.37,0:10:20.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Invisible writing, used to hide private information in public places.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.61,0:10:22.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's common.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.88,0:10:29.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On internet home-pages, people do\Nthis to hide information from others.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.19,0:10:34.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, why would Itakura-san use it on his own diary?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.39,0:10:40.13,Signs,,0,0,0,,I'm tired...\NAt this rate, I may be killed...\NSometime in the near future... {Sign-Middle Paragraph}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.83,0:10:39.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was probably used to camouflage serious parts of the diary.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.56,0:10:43.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, Shinichi, could it be that he...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.23,0:10:46.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, there's no doubt he mentioned them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.04,0:10:53.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Advertsiment: A Device "looks like a door" than can capture light}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.28,0:10:58.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Professor?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.75,0:11:02.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.12,0:11:03.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Professor?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.80,0:11:17.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He started using the invisible writing\Nten days after that man visited him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.33,0:11:19.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see them in order.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.87,0:11:22.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The entry from March 20th:
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.31,0:11:26.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"The pen an my desk has been moved 5cm again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.34,0:11:30.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I'm almost positive someone has been sneaking into my office."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.35,0:11:32.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The entry from April 15th:
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.25,0:11:35.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Now someone has broke into my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.78,0:11:37.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"The police won't take me seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.59,0:11:42.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Likely because nothing was stolen or damaged."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.49,0:11:45.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The entry from June 11th:
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.99,0:11:50.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I changed the lock and set up a security camera."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.03,0:11:55.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,July 6th: "Who are you!? Show yourself!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.87,0:11:59.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For the December 19th entry, it says:
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.97,0:12:02.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I'm tired, and at this rate, will be killed in the near future."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.14,0:12:10.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On January 6th: "To escape this fear,\NI left a message in the desk saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.89,0:12:14.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,," 'l agreed to your demands.'
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.29,0:12:18.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On January 8th: "To my surprise I've already gotten a reply.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.66,0:12:24.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"The intruder left a message on a piece of paper as I did before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.60,0:12:29.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"It only -O.K.- red and had a phone number written on it."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.57,0:12:36.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"This 'red' is probably blood... I wander if they're\N trying to tell me that... I'll lose my life?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.98,0:12:43.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On January 23rd: "I finally decided on the matter. I decided\Nto call the number without reporting it to the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.79,0:12:49.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"The one who answered was a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.96,0:12:52.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"A woman who speaks as if she were a queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.66,0:13:00.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Her only demand was for me to finish the computer program\NI had abandoned, and gave me one year to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.47,0:13:02.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"She would pay a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.77,0:13:06.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"This woman must be working with\Nthat giant from not too long ago."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.11,0:13:13.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For the February 13th entry: "They changed our\Nmethod of communication to electronic mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.08,0:13:18.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"l decided to agree to their demands under two conditions:
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.12,0:13:23.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"They must pay me through a bank transfer in\Nadvance, and they can't follow me around."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.16,0:13:26.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The December 22nd entry:
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.43,0:13:28.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.26,0:13:30.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"l refuse to finish it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.83,0:13:35.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"l know this program mustn't be completed,\Nnot because of my vision...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.53,0:13:38.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"But for humanity's sake."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.94,0:13:41.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For humanity's sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.44,0:13:45.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,February 9th: "The due date is coming soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.18,0:13:56.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I've decided to run. I'll leave the incomplete software\Nand their check near the computer at my cottage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.92,0:14:04.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"They'll be sending an e-mail at midnight five days from now,\Nwhich should-specify when and where deliver the program.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.39,0:14:06.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"l have to leave the country before then."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.80,0:14:11.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This entry is from four days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.77,0:14:14.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means that mail will be arriving tonight in three hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.47,0:14:21.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If seems that Itakura-san was only taking those game\Ncontracts so he could get money to leave the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.11,0:14:26.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like there's one final invisible message.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.32,0:14:35.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"February' 10th: "I wonder what they were\Ngoing to do with this program...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.69,0:14:41.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"l can't stop thinking about the strange\Nthings that woman said over the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.93,0:14:47.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Right, when I was finally tired of her queen-like mentality,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.67,0:14:53.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"l asked her who the hell she thought she\Nwas, to which she only replied in English...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.44,0:14:57.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"We can be both of God and the Devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.31,0:15:03.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Since we are trying raise the dead against the stream of time."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.98,0:15:05.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What'd you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.35,0:15:10.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"We can be both of God and the Devil, since...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.16,0:15:15.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"We're trying to raise the dead against the stream of time."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.30,0:15:18.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Haibara!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.60,0:15:19.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ai-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.93,0:15:24.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is that? Are you all reading some\Nfantasy story about a wizard?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.67,0:15:26.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.04,0:15:30.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've gotten hooked on a foreign story.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.65,0:15:34.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And? Why is Kudo-kun here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.08,0:15:37.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me? I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.78,0:15:42.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here for my new invention, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.16,0:15:44.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.06,0:15:50.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I call it the "Anywhere Ball Inflation Belt".
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.80,0:15:54.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like an ordinary belt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.97,0:15:55.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.70,0:15:58.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if you turn the and press the button..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.84,0:16:04.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You get a soccer ball
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.61,0:16:06.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A-Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.51,0:16:09.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can any amount of criminals with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.58,0:16:11.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, more like a couple...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.18,0:16:15.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can only stay inflated ten seconds after leaving the belt...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.59,0:16:17.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since it's made of a special material.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.99,0:16:19.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.89,0:16:20.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.53,0:16:26.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's very elastic though, you can make it\Nbigger than a balloon with mare gas!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.97,0:16:29.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.77,0:16:32.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You guys are stupid, I'm going bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.04,0:16:38.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, what do we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.98,0:16:41.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.28,0:16:46.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll go to Itakura-san's cottage and get that computer program.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.28,0:16:49.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can open the e-mail on his computer, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.99,0:16:53.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That e-mail they're going to send to Itokura-san at midnight!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.16,0:17:01.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How did you know Itakura-san's cottage was in Gunma?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.27,0:17:07.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When those three game company employees came\Nto Uncle, they mentioned places he could be at.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.44,0:17:13.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They mentioned this among some other places.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.38,0:17:19.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But is this alright? They could be planning to ambush him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.68,0:17:26.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Itakura-san made them\Npromise they wouldn't follow him around.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.29,0:17:33.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he was so observant that he noticed a pen being\Nmoved 5cm, they definitely wouldn't follow him up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.30,0:17:40.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true, they wouldn't want him to stop early and not finish it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.97,0:17:47.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So now our primary concern is as to whether the news of\NItakura-san's death has aired on TV or the radio yet, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.31,0:17:50.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's something we don't have to worry about either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.95,0:17:56.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At least for now, every news station is\Nairing news about those jewel robbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.62,0:18:02.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What concerns me is the last entry on the diary.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.96,0:18:05.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that "We can be both of God and the Devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.63,0:18:11.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Since we're trying to raise the dead against the stream of time."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.30,0:18:13.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.87,0:18:20.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Professor. Could it be that the drug\NHaibara was developing was...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.28,0:18:23.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It couldn't have been for zombies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.02,0:18:28.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.82,0:18:32.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Humans can't move against the stream of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.02,0:18:37.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If humans try to resist that, there will be punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.29,0:18:41.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? What punishment?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.33,0:18:48.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.50,0:18:53.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright, how can we get in?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.54,0:18:56.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.48,0:19:00.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where did you get the key?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.65,0:19:02.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was hidden behind the steps.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.78,0:19:06.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Remember, the diary told us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.72,0:19:10.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Il mentioned a friend calling his cottage\Nfor the first time in five years.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.46,0:19:17.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is actually to signal to friends that\Nthere's a key near the cottage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.63,0:19:19.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.77,0:19:23.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it obvious to keep it here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.64,0:19:26.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why he did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.91,0:19:33.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They would never figure their important program\Nwould be in such an obvious place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.91,0:19:37.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And if Oakura-san didn't answer the mail he was told to expect,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.35,0:19:44.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They would immediately come to this place,\Nfinding the program and check by the computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.36,0:19:47.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This way, Itakura-san would be able\N to get away without them knowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.59,0:19:52.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinichi, it's almost time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.63,0:19:53.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.20,0:19:57.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright, it's time to uncover the men in black.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.30,0:20:00.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Show me your true selves.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.17,0:20:04.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is it! The mail!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.94,0:20:06.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright, if I open this...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.31,0:20:10.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Password!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.15,0:20:13.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's counting down quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.22,0:20:15.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.72,0:20:19.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The mail disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.86,0:20:24.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn! It was programmed to disappear\Nif 'he password wasn't entered in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.59,0:20:28.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, could they know that we failed to open it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.97,0:20:29.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.77,0:20:33.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aside from that, they may know it came from this computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.64,0:20:39.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do we do? They may figure out that\Nsomething happened to itakura-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.81,0:20:40.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Shinichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.38,0:20:43.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.49,0:21:00.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I cannot come to the phone right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.00,0:21:08.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please leave a message after the beep.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.74,0:21:14.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yo, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.24,0:21:16.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vodka!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.31,0:21:19.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know you're there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.35,0:21:25.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means, they must have found out that\Nwe failed to open their e-mail at this cabin!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.55,0:21:26.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.15,0:21:29.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, they've been carefully...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.09,0:21:32.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Observing Itakura-san's cottage from a distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.56,0:21:34.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What'd you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.43,0:21:39.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was nearly certain that they wouldn't expect\NItakura-san would open the mail here,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.20,0:21:42.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Due to the insecurity of this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.54,0:21:47.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, that means we won't be able to escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.47,0:21:48.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, answer me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.58,0:21:52.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know you're in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.91,0:21:54.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Shinichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.28,0:21:59.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You better pick up the phone. Itakura-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.06,0:22:04.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.99,0:22:10.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You going to answer? Hey!
